{
  "stem": "4289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And obviously, they got a picture of my mother with the children sitting on her lap, both twins, which I recognized.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I figured out which one is the girl, which one is the boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every time I look at the picture, I was thinking, where is my twin?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I survived, there has to be possibility that one of them at least survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I thought, they had to survive together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the things I heard about my sister, that she was a very smart-- you know, street smart girl, they told me, the landlady, when I came and visit her, that Genia could go in front of the long line, and sneak in, and get her portion of food, or milk, or whatever, and bring to the house like that.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a really hard question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Adam asked me the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't remember father looking for anybody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he believed that they did not survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1949, he made me a birth certificate, but never made a birth certificate for Adam.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was like a non-existing, and-- or-- or for my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He thought that if my sister was alive, she would know where she lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She would come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother is probably not alive, because he was a boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was his theory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I went to school to get my-- you know--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--diploma every year, I had to have my birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally, he went to-- he wrote somebody to Sosnowiec, a witness from our neighborhood, some neighbor, and asked to go to court and be witness that I was born in 1939, May 3rd, and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was very little mention about my brother, only that I am from twins.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
